'''克卜勒20'''（{{lang en|'''Kepler-20'''}}）是一個距離地球950光年的恆星<ref name=Nature-20111220 />，位於[[天琴座|天琴座]]，它的行星系統有5顆行星<ref name="NASA-20111220">{{cite web |last=Johnson |first=Michele |title=NASA Discovers First Earth-size Planets Beyond Our Solar System |url=http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/kepler/news/kepler-20-system.html |publisher=[[NASA|NASA]] |date=20 December 2011 |accessdate=2011-12-20 |archive-date=2019-05-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190504012546/https://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/kepler/news/kepler-20-system.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其中兩顆為[[類地行星|類地行星]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theguardian.com/science/2011/dec/20/planets-earth-like-exoplanet-solar-system |title=Two new planets are most Earth-like ever seen – but hot as hell - The Guardian |accessdate=2013-12-06 |archive-date=2013-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131212002054/http://www.theguardian.com/science/2011/dec/20/planets-earth-like-exoplanet-solar-system |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==恆星狀況==
克卜勒20的[[視星等|視星等]]為12.51<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ancientsuns.com/space-facts/space-news/kepler-20ef.php |title=Kepler-20e and Kepler-20f — 2 Earth-sized Planets - Ancient Suns |access-date=2013-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131211132745/http://www.ancientsuns.com/space-facts/space-news/kepler-20ef.php |archive-date=2013-12-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，因此不能僅以肉眼觀看，必須以口徑{{Convert|15|cm|in|sigfig=1|abbr=on}}以上望遠鏡觀測<ref name=sherrod_koed2003/>。該恆星的光度稍低於太陽，半徑是[[太陽半徑|太陽半徑]]的94%，質量是[[太陽質量|太陽質量]]的91%。克卜勒20光球層的[[有效溫度|有效溫度]]是稍低於太陽的5,466 K，因此其顏色為黃色，[[恆星光譜|恆星光譜]]分類是G8。<ref name=csiro/>截至2011年，目前尚不知該恆星是否為[[主序星|主序星]]，而它的[[金屬量|金屬量]]與太陽相當。它的年齡可能比太陽稍老，雖然誤差範圍相對較大<ref name=exoplanet/>。

