2011年12月20日<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://articles.latimes.com/2011/dec/20/science/la-sci-planets-20111221 |title=Two Earth-sized planets found orbiting star Kepler-20 - Los Angeles Times |accessdate=2013-12-06 |archive-date=2013-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131217204222/http://articles.latimes.com/2011/dec/20/science/la-sci-planets-20111221 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[克卜勒太空望遠鏡|克卜勒太空望遠鏡]]團隊報告了首次發現體積與地球相若的行星[[克卜勒20e|克卜勒20e]]<ref name="Kepler20e-20111220">{{cite web |author=[[NASA|NASA Staff]] |title=Kepler: A Search For Habitable Planets - Kepler-20e |url=http://kepler.nasa.gov/Mission/discoveries/kepler20e/ |date=20 December 2011 |publisher=[[NASA|NASA]] |accessdate=2011-12-23 |archive-date=2017-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170331081504/https://kepler.nasa.gov/Mission/discoveries/kepler20e/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>和[[克卜勒20f|克卜勒20f]]<ref name="Kepler20f-20111220">{{cite web |author=[[NASA|NASA Staff]] |title=Kepler: A Search For Habitable Planets - Kepler-20f |url=http://kepler.nasa.gov/Mission/discoveries/kepler20f/ |date=20 December 2011 |publisher=[[NASA|NASA]] |accessdate=2011-12-23 |archive-date=2017-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170331125125/https://kepler.nasa.gov/Mission/discoveries/kepler20f/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>環繞[[類太陽恆星|類太陽恆星]]<ref name="Nature-20111220">{{cite web |last=Hand |first=Eric |title=Kepler discovers first Earth-sized exoplanets |url=http://www.nature.com/news/kepler-discovers-first-earth-sized-exoplanets-1.9688 |date=20 December 2011 |publisher=[[自然_(期刊)|Nature]] |accessdate=2011-12-20 |archive-date=2012-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120104125558/http://www.nature.com/news/kepler-discovers-first-earth-sized-exoplanets-1.9688 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="NASA-20111220" />克卜勒20公轉<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://kepler.nasa.gov/news/nasakeplernews/index.cfm?FuseAction=ShowNews&NewsID=172 |title=Kepler-20 system: 5 planets including two that are Earth-size - NASA |access-date=2013-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131211202207/http://kepler.nasa.gov/news/nasakeplernews/index.cfm?FuseAction=ShowNews&NewsID=172 |archive-date=2013-12-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

根據[[美國航空航天局|美國航空航天局]]的報告，這兩顆[[類地行星|類地行星]]距離[[適居帶|適居帶]]過遠<ref name="Nature-20111220" />，表面溫度分別是760和427°C，而這兩顆行星的軌道半徑都小於[[水星|水星]]軌道<ref name="Moskowitz">{{cite news |last=Moskowitz |first=Clara |title=First Ever 'Earth-Sized' Alien Planets Discovered |url=http://www.foxnews.com/scitech/2011/12/20/first-ever-earth-sized-alien-planets-discovered/ |date=20 December 2011 |publisher=[[福斯新聞頻道|Fox News Channel]] |accessdate=2011-12-20 |archive-date=2011-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111225130859/http://www.foxnews.com/scitech/2011/12/20/first-ever-earth-sized-alien-planets-discovered/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。克卜勒20在之前已發現有三個海王星大小的行星：[[克卜勒20b|克卜勒20b]]、[[克卜勒20c|克卜勒20c]]和[[克卜勒20d|克卜勒20d]]。而該系統中距離母恆星距離由近到遠是 b-e-c-f-d。而這些行星的軌道所在範圍相當於水星環繞太陽軌道之內<ref name="NYT-20111220">{{cite news |last=Overbye |first=Dennis |title=Two Earth-Size Planets Are Discovered |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/12/21/science/space/nasas-kepler-spacecraft-discovers-2-earth-size-planets.html |date=20 December 2011 |publisher=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]] |accessdate=2011-12-21 |archive-date=2013-01-26 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6DxnWghEN?url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/12/21/science/space/nasas-kepler-spacecraft-discovers-2-earth-size-planets.html?_r=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Space-20111220">{{cite web |last=Tate |first=Karl |url=http://www.space.com/13987-earth-size-alien-planets-kepler-22e-infographic.html |title=At Last, Earth-Sized Alien Worlds (Infographic) |publisher=Space.com |date=20 December 2011 |accessdate=2011-12-21 |archive-date=2012-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120106084343/http://www.space.com/13987-earth-size-alien-planets-kepler-22e-infographic.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

該行星系統和太陽系的不同之處是該系統的氣體巨行星和類地行星是交錯排列的。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://arxiv.org/abs/1112.4550 |title=Two Earth-sized planets orbiting Kepler-20 - Cornell University Library |accessdate=2013-12-06 |archive-date=2016-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821210026/http://arxiv.org/abs/1112.4550 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
 
