===克卜勒20e和f===
克卜勒20e和f都是[[太陽系外行星|系外]][[類地行星|類地行星]]<ref>[http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/vnfv/ncurrent/full/nature10780.html Two Earth-sized planets orbiting Kepler-20 - Nature]</ref>，它們的質量與地球相若：e的質量為地球質量的0.39–1.67倍<ref name="kepler20e">{{Cite web |url=http://kepler.nasa.gov/Mission/discoveries/kepler20e/ |title=Kepler-20e - NASA |accessdate=2013-12-06 |archive-date=2017-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170331081504/https://kepler.nasa.gov/Mission/discoveries/kepler20e/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而f的質量則為地球質量的0.66–3.04倍<ref name="kepler20f">{{Cite web |url=http://kepler.nasa.gov/Mission/discoveries/kepler20f/ |title=Kepler-20f - NASA |accessdate=2013-12-06 |archive-date=2017-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170331125125/https://kepler.nasa.gov/Mission/discoveries/kepler20f/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而它們的規模更與地球非常相近：e的半徑為地球半徑的0.868倍<ref name="kepler20e"/>，而f的半徑則為地球半徑的1.034倍<ref name="kepler20f"/>，這顯示e和f都可能是一個[[超級地球|超級地球]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/kepler/news/kepler-20-system.html |title=NASA Discovers First Earth-size Planets Beyond Our Solar System - NASA |accessdate=2011-12-20 |archive-date=2019-05-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190504012546/https://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/kepler/news/kepler-20-system.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>e是第一個被發現圍繞著類太陽恆星公轉，且規模比地球小的太陽系外行星<ref name="kepler20e"/>；而f則是至今人類已知大小最接近地球的太陽系外行星<ref name="kepler20f"/>。e和f的[[半長軸|半長軸]]分別為0.0630天文單位<ref name="kepler20e"/>和0.1370天文單位<ref name="kepler20f"/>，而因為過於接近母星，所以它們的表面溫度介乎於705 K和1040 K之間。<ref name="kepler20e"/>

===克卜勒20b、c和d===
克卜勒20b、c和d都是[[太陽系外行星|系外]][[氣體巨行星|氣體巨行星]]，它們的質量均大於地球很多：b、c和d的質量分別為地球質量的8.7倍<ref name="kepler20b">{{Cite web |url=http://kepler.nasa.gov/Mission/discoveries/kepler20b/ |title=Kepler-20b - NASA |access-date=2013-12-06 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6I11derQB?url=http://kepler.nasa.gov/Mission/discoveries/kepler20b/ |archive-date=2013-07-10 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>、16.1倍<ref name="kepler20c">{{Cite web |url=http://kepler.nasa.gov/Mission/discoveries/kepler20c/ |title=Kepler-20c - NASA |access-date=2013-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120503214356/http://kepler.nasa.gov/Mission/discoveries/kepler20c/ |archive-date=2012-05-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>和20.1倍<ref name="kepler20d">{{Cite web |url=http://kepler.nasa.gov/Mission/discoveries/kepler20d/ |title=Kepler-20d - NASA |access-date=2013-12-06 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6I11wzUhZ?url=http://kepler.nasa.gov/Mission/discoveries/kepler20d/ |archive-date=2013-07-10 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。而它們的規模則介乎於地球和[[海王星|海王星]]之間：b、c和d的半徑分別為地球半徑的1.91倍<ref name="kepler20b"/>、3.07倍<ref name="kepler20c"/>和2.75倍<ref name="kepler20d"/>。它們的大小均比海王星（半徑為地球半徑的3.883倍）小，但比地球大，因此被歸類為[[迷你海王星|迷你海王星]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://iopscience.iop.org/0004-637X/749/1/15 |title=KEPLER-20: A SUN-LIKE STAR WITH THREE SUB-NEPTUNE EXOPLANETS AND TWO EARTH-SIZE CANDIDATES - IOP science |accessdate=2013-12-06 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714024423/http://iopscience.iop.org/0004-637X/749/1/15/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>b是至今被發現體積最大，且密度接近地球密度的系外行星<ref name="kepler20b"/>。b、c和d的[[半長軸|半長軸]]分別為0.04537天文單位<ref name="kepler20b"/>、0.0930天文單位<ref name="kepler20c"/>和0.3453天文單位<ref name="kepler20d"/>，而因為過於接近母星，所以它們的表面溫度最高能達5,466 K<ref name="kepler20b"/>。而因為其表面溫度如此高<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cosis.net/abstracts/EGS02/04469/EGS02-A-04469.pdf |title=Hot Neptunes: A Key To Giant Planet Formation |accessdate=2013-12-06 |archive-date=2019-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190617152111/https://www.cosis.net/abstracts/EGS02/04469/EGS02-A-04469.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cosis.net/abstracts/EGU2008/07657/EGU2008-A-07657.pdf |title=Oligarchic formation of hot Neptunes |accessdate=2013-12-06 |archive-date=2017-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171006211803/http://www.cosis.net/abstracts/EGU2008/07657/EGU2008-A-07657.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，所以它們被歸類為[[熱海王星|熱海王星]]。<ref>{{citation |url=http://www.centauri-dreams.org/?p=1263 |title=Transiting 'Hot Neptune' Found |date=2007-05-16 |publisher=[[Tau_Zero_Foundation|Centauri Dreams]] |accessdate=2013-12-06 |archive-date=2013-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131210214725/http://www.centauri-dreams.org/?p=1263 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://arxiv.org/abs/1112.4514 |title=Kepler-20: A Sun-like Star with Three Sub-Neptune Exoplanets and Two Earth-size Candidates - Cornell University Library |accessdate=2013-12-06 |archive-date=2017-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170510131225/https://arxiv.org/abs/1112.4514 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

